====================================
Populous - News Publication Platform
====================================

Built on top of the awesome `Django`_ Web framework, `Populous`_ is a platform
for developing news content websites.  Populous is being funded by a grant from
the Knight Foundation.

Populous is still in very heavy development, so for now use it at your own
risk.  Be aware that things will change as we continue to improve Populous.
Feel free to contribute and get involved! 

.. _`Django`: http://www.djangoproject.com/
.. _`Populous`: http://populousproject.com/